  "body": "### Description\nWhen syncing post merge, the head block won't update if the execution client is still syncing which will make it look like Teku's sync has stalled.  We need to update the syncing log lines to include both the verified head and the optimistic head in some way to show users that Teku is progressing but we're still waiting on the execution engine to complete verification.",
